'''HD 20781'''是一個視星等8等的[[黃矮星|黃矮星]]，位於[[天爐座|天爐座]]，距離地球117光年。

==概述==
HD 20781和另一顆恆星[[HD_20782|HD 20782]]組成距離相當遠的聯星系統。這兩顆恆星有各自的行星系，且軌道形狀是S形。這是第一個成員星都有各自行星系統的[[聯星|聯星]]系<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aanda.org/index.php?option=com_article&access=bibcode&Itemid=129&bibcode=2007A%2526A...462..345DFUL |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-23 |archive-date=2019-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120093655/https://www.aanda.org/index.php?option=com_article&access=bibcode&Itemid=129&bibcode=2007A%2526A...462..345DFUL |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Notes for star HD 20781 |cite web|url=http://exoplanet.eu/star.php?st=HD+20781|author=Schneider, J|work=The Extrasolar Planets Encyclopaedia|accessdate=2011-09-12|archive-date=2013-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130314215628/http://exoplanet.eu/catalog/?f=%27HD%2020781%27+in+name|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite arXiv|eprint=1109.2497|class=astro-ph|title=The HARPS search for southern extra-solar planets XXXIV. Occurrence, mass distribution and orbital properties of super-Earths and Neptune-mass planets|author=Mayor, M. Marmier,M.  Lovis,C.  Udry,S.  Ségransan,D.  Pepe,F.  Benz,W.  Bertaux,J.-L.  Bouchy,F. Dumusque, G.  Curto,Lo  Mordasini,C. Queloz,D.  Santos,N. C. ''et al.''|year=2011}}</ref>。

